      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an affordable price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining on the carpets from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts up every time and the transmission shifts as it should, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that has been used consistently and is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
