    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral dynamics. Mechanical integrity is a priority; the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the suspension maintains its original kinematic precision. While the exterior shows light patina, the chassis remains stiff and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically honest machine ready for spirited canyon carving.",
